Immigration Battle

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Shari Robertson and Michael Camerini, published by PBS broadcasted as part of PBS Frontline series in 2015 - English narration
 
http://docuwiki.net/images/6/67/Immigration-Battle-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

Inside the hard-fought battles and secret negotiations over immigration reform on Capitol Hill. Explore President Obama's push for policy changes that could impact the fate of millions and define what it means to be American for decades to come.
